---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Services | Petrol Nexus" path="/services">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p>From exploration to distribution, we provide end-to-end support for petroleum and energy operations.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card"><h3>Reservoir Engineering</h3><p>Production planning, reserve optimization, and analytics.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Pipeline Integrity</h3><p>Inspection, corrosion management, and preventive interventions.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Refinery Support</h3><p>Turnaround planning, controls tuning, and process reliability.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>HSE Programs</h3><p>Safety frameworks, audits, and incident prevention systems.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Energy Logistics</h3><p>Marine, rail, and terminal coordination for global delivery.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Digital Operations</h3><p>Control-room visibility, alerts, and predictive maintenance.</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
